task.summary: Updates - Espresso Unit Testing - Create Event now works again
Updates to CreateEvent to get the plumbing working. Web service call is working using empty strings. Next push will include user input values.
Updated variables names in Event and CreateEvent

added sport_picker.xml and SportPickerFragment which are the intermediary screens between the map and create_event. it now supports picking a sport to load the correct layout. notes are in the code to help with the next phase. edits to CreateEventFragment include getting the arguments from the main activity as well as the SportPickerFragmenet. added sport (pictures) of running, weightlifting, and yoga.
updated sport picker fragment and xml page to be a transparent pop up. added all new geotags as well.
updated sport picker fragment and xml page from using px to dp. moved create event icon on map to bottom right corner from center
Current version including json data transfer in URLConnection. Updates to Event and Users. Updates to app variables. First update of a sequence that includes fixing a new build.
Integration updates - Map now populating correctly - Create Event working - Event List working - User Profile working
Integration updates - Updates to URLConnection for deletes
